{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/ViewEnvironmentPropagating\/environment"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui\/viewenvironmentpropagating\/environment"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:17ViewEnvironmentUI0aB11PropagatingPAAE11environment0aB0AEVvp","title":"environment","extendedModule":"ViewEnvironmentUI","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"environment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ViewEnvironment","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"}],"modules":[{"name":"ViewEnvironmentUI"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI","doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/ViewEnvironmentPropagating"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and provide those overrides in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customize(environment:)"},{"type":"text","text":". E.g.:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func customize(environment: inout ViewEnvironment) {","    environment.traits.mode = .dark","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property gets the environment by recursively walking to the root of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation path, and applying customizations on the way back down. The invalidation path may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interrupted if a node has set it’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentAncestor"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", even if there is a node"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which specifies this node as an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentDescendant"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to update the return value of this variable and have those changes propagated through the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation hierarchy, conform to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setNeedsEnvironmentUpdate()"},{"type":"text","text":" and wait"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the system to call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"apply(context:)"},{"type":"text","text":" when appropriate (e.g. on the next layout pass for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclasses)."}]},{"style":"important","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"code":"UIViewController","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"UIView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" conformers "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"must","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" call "},{"code":"applyEnvironmentIfNeeded()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"viewWillLayoutSubviews()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"layoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" respectively."}]}],"name":"Important"}]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironment"},{"type":"text","text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy."}],"references":{"doc://ViewEnvironmentUI/documentation/ViewEnvironmentUI":{"abstract":[],"title":"ViewEnvironmentUI","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui"},"doc://ViewEnvironmentUI/documentation/ViewEnvironmentUI/ViewEnvironmentPropagating":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A node in a "},{"code":"ViewEnvironment","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" propagation tree."}],"url":"\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui\/viewenvironmentpropagating","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/ViewEnvironmentPropagating","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ViewEnvironmentPropagating","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironmentPropagating","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"ViewEnvironmentPropagating"},"doc://ViewEnvironmentUI/documentation/ViewEnvironmentUI/ViewEnvironmentPropagating/environment":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"environment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","text":"ViewEnvironment"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"ViewEnvironment","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy.","type":"text"}